Title: Tempus Fugit (1)
Plot: While celebrating Scully's 33rd birthday, a strange woman informs Mulder that NICAP member Max Fenig (see Fallen Angel) has recently died in a plane crash. After a visit to the crash site and finding Max's body with radiation burns on it, Mulder suggests that the plane was intercepted by a UFO and is rapidly being covered up by the military.
GuestStars: Joe Spano, Tom O'Brien, Scott Bellis, Chilton Crane, Greg Michaels, Robert Moloney, Felicia Shulman, Rick Dobran, Jerry Schram, David Palffy, Mark Wilson, Marek Wiedman, Maria Luisa Cianni
